Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class MemberDatabase

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.MemberDatabase
public class MemberDatabase extends Object
MemberDatabase class contain methods to generate member list and perform memberlist operation. This class generate member list as well as add/remove member from list and print the list in variety way.
Author:
Sihua Zhou
